message: "If you use these materials, please cite them as follows."
authors:
- family-names: "Boushey"
  given-names: "Geoffrey"
  affiliation: "UCSF Library"
title: "Document Analysis with Python, SQL, and AI: Workshop Series"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2024-05-13
url: "https://github.com/geoffswc/UCSF-DSOS-Python-SQL-Workshops"
abstract: >-
  A scaffolded curriculum for the UCSF Library workshop series, transitioning 
  from foundational Python and SQL to advanced machine learning and 
  AI-driven research. The repository demonstrates a modern workflow: 
  moving from manual coding to auditing AI-generated models for 
  COVID-19 prediction, sentiment analysis, and automated document 
  transcription using local GenAI.
keywords:
